      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle offers a straightforward, budget-conscious way to get on the road. It presents as a sensible choice for a buyer seeking basic utility and strong value, with solid potential as an everyday runabout, starter vehicle, or backup car. Priced to reflect its condition, it stands out as an affordable opportunity for someone who appreciates honest motoring.",
