    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a practical runaround. It\u2019s priced to reflect its condition and could be a great fit for the right buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. If you want something honest, inexpensive, and worth a look, this one may surprise you.",
