      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a tough-running powertrain and good bones where it counts. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for someone who wants an affordable commuter, shop truck, or weekend fixer. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from an older used vehicle rather than hidden surprises. Cosmetics and overall condition are rough, so come in expecting blemishes, age, and needed attention, but for the money it\u2019s a usable, mechanically serviceable vehicle with plenty of value left for the right buyer.",
      "price": 4900.0,
